1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,891
Chapter 9 Think Right Toward People Here is a basic rule for winning success.

2
00:00:08,001 --> 00:00:10,450
Let's mark it in the mind and remember it.

3
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:15,331
The rule is, success depends on the support of other people.

4
00:00:15,841 --> 00:00:20,851
The only hurdle between you and what you want to be is the support of others.

5
00:00:21,281 --> 00:00:22,691
Look at it this way.

6
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:26,930
An executive depends on people to carry out his instructions.

7
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:32,611
If they don't, the company president will fire the executive, not the employees.

8
00:00:32,961 --> 00:00:36,210
A salesman depends on people to buy his product.

9
00:00:36,241 --> 00:00:38,611
If they don't, the salesman fails.

10
00:00:38,881 --> 00:00:45,571
Likewise, a college dean depends on professors to carry forward his educational program.

11
00:00:45,921 --> 00:00:49,011
A politician depends on voters to elect him.

12
00:00:49,201 --> 00:00:52,691
A writer depends on people to read what he writes.

13
00:00:53,041 --> 00:01:03,491
A chain store magnate got to be a chain store magnate because employees accepted his leadership and consumers accepted his merchandising program.

14
00:01:03,841 --> 00:01:12,450
There were times in history when a person could gain a position of authority through force and hold it with force and or threats of force.

15
00:01:12,641 --> 00:01:19,491
In those days, a man either cooperated with the leader or risked literally losing his head.

16
00:01:20,001 --> 00:01:26,691
But today, remember, a person either supports you willingly or he doesn't support you at all.

17
00:01:27,681 --> 00:01:34,371
Now it's time to ask, granted, I depend on others in order to achieve the success I want,

18
00:01:34,481 --> 00:01:39,571
but what must I do to get these people to support me and accept my leadership?

19
00:01:40,081 --> 00:01:45,170
The answer, wrapped up in one phrase, is, think right toward people.

20
00:01:45,441 --> 00:01:49,170
Think right toward people, and they will like and support you.

21
00:01:49,361 --> 00:01:51,250
This chapter shows how.

22
00:01:52,321 --> 00:01:56,211
Thousands of times daily a scene like this takes place.

